##### Add Memories
POST https://api.mem0.ai/v1/memories/
Authorization: Token {{mem0ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "this is a test message."
    }
  ],
  "user_id": "will",
  "app_id": "curl-test-001",
  "version": "v2"
}

