##### Get Memories
POST https://api.mem0.ai/v2/memories/
Authorization: Token {{mem0ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filters": {
    "AND": [
      { "user_id": "will" },
      { "app_id": "curl-test-001" },
      { "created_at": { "gte": "2025-11-01", "lte": "2025-11-12" } }
    ]
  }
}

##### Search Memories
POST https://api.mem0.ai/v2/memories/search/
Authorization: Token {{mem0ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is my name?",
  "filters": {
    "AND": [
      { "user_id": "will" },
      { "app_id": "curl-test-001" }
    ]
  },
  "top_k": "3",
  "threshold": "0.4"
}

